    Spare and minimalist, Sorensen evokes Danish modern design. The pared-down profile features slightly flared shelter arms and an expansive bench seat, the frame resting atop slim oak legs.

    ALSO AVAILABLE IN LEATHER

    undefined 90 undefined FabricS
    DETAILS
    • Frame handcrafted of kiln-dried solid hardwood
    • Reinforced joinery with corner blocking
    • Sinuous spring suspension with woven webbing seat
    • Square-cut legs crafted of oak
    • 5' and 6' sofas have 4 legs total
    • 7' and 8' sofas have 5 legs total; 9' sofa has 6 legs total
    • Foot finish varies by fabric color. View details.
    • Seat cushion and side cushions extend 1" to 1" beyond the front of the sofa frame
    • Seat cushion features polyfiber wrapped around a 4" foam core; coordinating side cushions are all polyfiber
    • 1 attached seat cushion/3 attached side cushions
    • Fabric and leather dye lots vary; pieces purchased at different times may not match exactly
    • Professional upholstery cleaning recommended. Vacuum with an upholstery attachment to remove dust. To minimize fading, avoid placing in direct sunlight.
    DIMENSIONS
    • Lengths: 5', 6', 7', 8', 9'
    • Depths: Classic 33", Luxe 39"
    • Frame Depths: Classic 31", Luxe 37"
    • Height: 26"
    • Frame Height: 25"
    • Seat Height: 18"
    • Arm Height: 25"
